    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense... so basically the bigger the debt, the more the interest just swallows up my payment. it feels pretty predatory when you put it that way, like there's something actively working to keep me stuck in debt. how do people actually get ahead of it then?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
